blog.name: angelofberlin2000
blog.title: Like a Rose trampled on the ground
blog.description:
In addition to the pain and the exhaustion, he recalled how waiting on the cross between takes became tedious. To fight the boredom, he listened to music on headphones. One particular song called "Above All" (Like a Rose ...) by Michael W. Smith helped him through his most difficult moments.

"It arrived when I was confused and angry. I didn't think I could go on. The song described how Jesus was rejected and alone. That thought took me to a place — it opened an interior door that held me while on the cross," an emotional Caviezel explained. "The experience of feeling rejected and alone as all those around me laughed while drinking their hot coffees, oblivious to what was occurring. Jesus must have felt like this — forsaken, rejected, alone, and despised. It helped me pray in a very deep way — to pray without words, to pray from the heart. The discomfort, the loneliness, the split shoulder, the raw flesh all forced me into the arms of God because I had nowhere else to go for a performance I knew I was unable to create."
Jim Caviezel, Shamelessly Catholic

summary: * let me go * John wick imagine
body:
* let me go * John wick imagine

“ excuse me, I need a room please ” I said as I ran into the holet and ran to the front desk stepping in front of the man purposely to hide from my recently ex boyfriend. “ excuse me ” the man said “ I’m sorry but you will have to have money ” the man behide the desk said “ CHERISH! ” I heard my ex boyfriend scream as he came through the door. i flinched and jump over the desk and put my legs up to my chest and silently cried I look up at the man who look down at me and i shook my head as i began to shake. “ please ” I begged. The man looks up and I hear the man I had step in front of say something but couldn’t make it out. “ hello how may I help you ? ” the man ask “ did you see a young woman run in here ? ” my ex ask “ no have you mr. Wick ? ” the man ask “ No I haven’t seen anyone i only just got here ” mr. Wick said i figured he was the one I step in front of. “ DAMN IT! ” my ex screamed and slap his hands on the counter I jump and began to shake I quickly put my hands over my mouth to quiet myself. “ sir I will have to ask you to leave if you continue to act like that. ” the man said “ go to hell..I’m leaving ” my ex said as I heard him leave. “ he’s gone now ms.” the man said i slowly look up and saw mr.wick staring at me as I look around and saw my ex had in fact left. “ westfall. cherish westfall thank you ” I said “ pleasure to meet you my name is Charon ” the man said as i look up at him and smiled that’s when we look over at mr. Wick “ is there a back exit ? ” I ask “ Yes I’ll show you but frist let me take care of mr. Wick ” charon said “ Oh right sorry Mr wick ” I said and slowly sat back down on the floor and waitted. “ alright cherish come along ” charon said “ thank you ” I said as I got up “ I’ll take her ” Mr wick said suddenly I look between the two “ I don’t know you mr wick And I have no idea what this place is but it’s so fancey ” I said “ my name is John wick and i can protect you from that ex ” John said “ johnathon think this through ” I heard another male voice call. I look over at him and he look like the boss you can feel the power he had. He was in his 50’s , he has salt and pepper hair , had green eyes.“ listen guys I don’t want to complicate things I have things going on too so charon show me the back exit ” I said that’s when I saw my ex and he saw me “CHERISH! ” I heard him call that’s when I saw johns face. “ johnathon think this through ” the male said as he slowly walk towards john.

I took off running down the hall I heard the yells from behide me but I just ran I felt my foot caught the wall as i turn a corner sharply and fell flat on my stomach I was dove on and i kicked and screamed as the person push my head against the floor I heard guns the bullet being loaded in the chamber I heard a whistle and we look up and saw guns being pointed at us. “ get off of her! ” John order my ex started to shake “ this is between me and her ” my ex said trying his best not to piss himself. “ you are in my building therefore she is my business now as my man said get off of her ” the male said my ex look down at me and i felt his brealth on my ear along with my body becoming wet and warm. “ I’ll be back bitch ” my ex said and threw my head down against the floor and slowly got off of me. I heard Snickers from everyone i tried to look around but all i saw was black dots. “ cherish he pissed all over you ” I heard john say i groaned and placed a hand on my forehead “ is it okay if I pick you up and take care of you ? ” John ask “ Yes ” i chocked out as i began to cry I felt john slowly pick me up as john ordered charon for clothes and a doctor for me he carried me to the elevator and we went up to whatever floor. John open the door and put me on my feet I had stop seeing black dots. “ you are going to be okay ” John said as he began to pull my shirt off but I punch his chest. “ sorry should have asked frist I’m sorry ” john said “ I’ll be in the bathroom ” I said as I walk to the bathroom not looking back as i closed the door I let out a breath and wash my face trying not to look at how beat up i was. “ cherish ” John said softly “ leave me alone ” I mutter as I look at myself I sat down and crawl on the floor to lean against the door.

“ cherish we need to see you so the doctor can take a look at you ” john said his voice was still calm and soft. I scoot up and was still sitting on the floor the door opens and john and the doctor came in. “ mr. Wick stay outside my name’s sully cherish. ” sully the doctor said I stood up. “ nice to meet you but I need to take a shower my ex pissed on me ” i said “ cherish you can’t not right now anyways ” sully said “ why not ? ” I asked “ because we need his dna ” sully said i stood there silently as sully began to look me over “ May I ? ” sully ask just as he ask there was a knock on the door “ I got you’re clothes ” john mutters from outside the door “ Thank you ” I said as I strip off my shirt as the door open all three of us stare at eachother “ GET OUT! ” I screamed as I blush john quickly drop the clothes and shut the door “ well that was embarrassing ” I mutter sully laughs “ young love ” sully said “ ew no even if he’s attractive. ” I said as I look away and look at the shower. “ I see just bruises so you should be fine just tasks some aspirin for the pain and rest ” sully said “ Thank you sully ” I said as I quickly turn on the water “ your welcome cherish ” sully said and sully open the door and closed it behide him i quickly strip off my clothes and got in the shower sighing at the hot water hit me.
